# MEMORY — Project Facts

Durable facts about *the work and the world* the agent operates in:
ongoing projects, key people, decisions, recurring topics. Loaded once per
session and wrapped in `<persistent_memory>` tags. Soft cap ~2,200 chars.

Maintained by the agent via the `memory` tool. Edit by hand freely.

Format: one fact per `§`-delimited block.

---

§ Working on: <project name> — <one-line description>
§ Stack: <e.g. Python, Pipecat, DeepSeek, Soniox>
§ Open question: <what's currently undecided>
